If something were to happen
to Cheng Ruoning now,

20
00:02:15,970 --> 00:02:17,680
people would know I was the mastermind,
wouldn't they?

21
00:02:17,680 --> 00:02:19,640
How could you come up with
such a stupid idea?

22
