Please spare my life, My Lord!

24
00:02:26,570 --> 00:02:27,290
Please spare my life, My Lord!

25
00:02:27,290 --> 00:02:29,020
Chief Matchmaker Fang is here!

26
00:02:30,710 --> 00:02:31,630
My Lord.

27
00:02:36,560 --> 00:02:37,590
Get out!

28
00:02:44,790 --> 00:02:47,320
Fang Yue,
I've asked you to come to the capital

29
00:02:48,070 --> 00:02:50,270
because I want you to suppress Shi Fa'ke

30
00:02:50,370 --> 00:02:51,770
and help me with my plans.

31
00:02:52,100 --> 00:02:54,560
But there has been no progress
after so long.

32
00:02:56,730 --> 00:02:58,300
I'm so disappointed in you.

33
00:02:58,500 --> 00:03:01,170
Shi Fa'ke
is indeed a capable marriage broker.

34
00:03:02,100 --> 00:03:03,030
What did you say?

35
00:03:03,180 --> 00:03:04,700
Her mind is pure,

36
00:03:04,740 --> 00:03:06,730
and she solely focuses on
being a good matchmaker.

37
00:03:06,730 --> 00:03:09,660
The simpler the person is, the more likely
she is to achieve great things.

38
00:03:09,660 --> 00:03:11,990
In terms of this,
I can't compare with her.

39
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:15,730
I'm full of selfish motives
and improper desires.

40
00:03:20,910 --> 00:03:23,280
Alright. Stop talking about this.

41
00:03:25,410 --> 00:03:27,490
With Cheng Ruoning's status like that,

42
00:03:27,490 --> 00:03:31,150
it doesn't matter if she refuses to
join Marquis Wu'an's Mansion.

43
00:03:32,590 --> 00:03:33,590
You may leave now.

44
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:45,540
What? Is there something else?

45
00:03:45,620 --> 00:03:46,430
My Lord.

46
00:03:47,430 --> 00:03:49,490
The fate of marriage is predestined.

47
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:51,470
It won't end well if you force it.

48
00:03:53,030 --> 00:03:54,300
Do you have to use marriage

49
00:03:54,300 --> 00:03:55,900
to get what you want?

50
