I'll take my leave now.

51
00:04:17,209 --> 00:04:19,709
[Cheng's Mansion]

52
00:04:22,590 --> 00:04:25,120
My Lady,
Marriage Broker Shi is here to visit.

53
00:04:26,090 --> 00:04:27,560
Marriage Broker Shi, Mr. Lu.

54
