during the matchmaking event.

72
00:05:08,640 --> 00:05:10,770
I'm afraid he won't let this go easily.

73
00:05:10,950 --> 00:05:12,410
As long as we still stay in the capital,

74
00:05:12,410 --> 00:05:14,780
