for Qiujiang and me anytime.

75
00:05:14,780 --> 00:05:16,100
I'm worried that next time,

76
00:05:16,100 --> 00:05:18,240
he'll hurt Qiujiang even worse.

77
00:05:18,530 --> 00:05:21,880
So I want to leave the capital.

78
00:05:21,950 --> 00:05:23,350
That's absolutely not okay.

79
00:05:23,350 --> 00:05:24,070
Ruoning.

80
00:05:24,610 --> 00:05:26,720
You've never left the capital
since childhood.

81
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:28,470
And all the Cheng family's assets
are here.

82
00:05:28,470 --> 00:05:30,080
Do you know what it means to you

83
