96
00:05:58,990 --> 00:06:00,990
he has become even more aggressive.

97
00:06:01,520 --> 00:06:03,060
Is there really no way

98
00:06:03,210 --> 00:06:04,610
to get rid of his threats?

99
00:06:05,510 --> 00:06:08,030
All these matters
are caused by Marquis Wu'an.

100
00:06:08,030 --> 00:06:10,160
Is there really no one who can stop him?

101
00:06:10,810 --> 00:06:13,270
Actually,
there is someone who can stop him.

102
00:06:16,740 --> 00:06:17,710
Who is it?

103
00:06:21,830 --> 00:06:23,490
I cannot reveal such secrets.

104
00:06:27,260 --> 00:06:28,070
Ke.

105
00:06:28,390 --> 00:06:29,720
This is a serious matter.

106
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:30,910
Though I cannot tell you,

107
00:06:30,910 --> 00:06:32,180
I can promise you that

108
00:06:32,320 --> 00:06:34,180
I will do my best to work things out.

109
00:06:34,180 --> 00:06:35,100
Before that,

110
00:06:35,360 --> 00:06:37,090
I'll ask Lu Yi
to protect Young Master Qiujiang

111
00:06:37,090 --> 00:06:38,020
and Miss Cheng.

112
00:06:39,050 --> 00:06:39,820
Don't worry.

113
00:06:41,340 --> 00:06:42,290
I got it.

114
00:06:43,180 --> 00:06:44,010
Thank you, Lu.

