172
00:10:07,960 --> 00:10:08,950
Miss Cheng.

173
00:10:09,430 --> 00:10:11,850
I understand it's difficult for you
to decide now.

174
00:10:11,850 --> 00:10:14,110
But this is the only solution we have now.

175
00:10:14,110 --> 00:10:16,000
If the Cheng family
is still extremely wealthy,

176
00:10:16,000 --> 00:10:17,580
Marquis Wu'an
will certainly do everything he can

177
00:10:17,580 --> 00:10:19,860
to seize your family's fortune
for himself.

178
00:10:19,860 --> 00:10:21,930
If you and Young Master Qiujiang
are not under protection,

179
00:10:21,930 --> 00:10:23,700
he'll certainly find a chance
to take revenge.

180
00:10:23,700 --> 00:10:24,410
I know.

181
00:10:25,380 --> 00:10:27,330
But all of this is the family property

182
00:10:27,330 --> 00:10:29,610
my father has gained
through his lifelong efforts.

183
00:10:29,610 --> 00:10:30,110
I...

184
00:10:30,640 --> 00:10:32,770
I really can't make this decision now.

185
00:10:33,090 --> 00:10:34,880
Could I have some time to think about it?

186
00:10:34,880 --> 00:10:36,610
Miss Cheng, I understand how you feel.

187
00:10:36,610 --> 00:10:38,820
This is just a piece of advice
from Ke and me.

188
00:10:38,820 --> 00:10:40,060
But in the end,

189
00:10:40,380 --> 00:10:42,380
you're the one to make the decision.

190
00:10:46,780 --> 00:10:48,310
Whatever your decision is,

191
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:49,770
we will support you.

192
00:10:55,560 --> 00:10:57,670
My Lord! Bad news, My Lord!

193
00:10:57,810 --> 00:10:59,210
Why are you so flustered?

194
00:10:59,340 --> 00:11:02,240
The Cheng family has changed the names

195
00:11:02,260 --> 00:11:03,410
of all their shops today.

196
00:11:03,410 --> 00:11:06,560
The Cheng family has donated
all their assets to the country.

197
00:11:06,560 --> 00:11:09,250
Now they've become royal merchants.

198
00:11:09,490 --> 00:11:10,490
Royal merchants?

199
00:11:11,250 --> 00:11:14,530
The Cheng family's assets
now belong to the royal family?

200
00:11:14,680 --> 00:11:16,750
I've heard that Cheng Ruoning

201
00:11:16,780 --> 00:11:18,840
has donated all the family property.

202
00:11:19,170 --> 00:11:20,630
She said the purpose was to

203
00:11:20,650 --> 00:11:23,750
bring prosperity to Liang State
and provide funds for the army.

204
00:11:23,750 --> 00:11:24,880
That's ridiculous!

205
00:11:25,860 --> 00:11:26,490
So you mean

206
00:11:26,530 --> 00:11:28,360
before I can get the money,

207
00:11:28,640 --> 00:11:31,040
now it's possessed by that person instead?

208
00:11:32,020 --> 00:11:34,000
Cheng Ruoning is just a woman.

209
00:11:34,490 --> 00:11:36,620
How would she come up with such an idea?

210
00:11:37,030 --> 00:11:39,490
Lu Chi and Shi Fa'ke
must be the masterminds.

211
00:11:39,710 --> 00:11:41,320
If I don't kill Cheng Ruoning,

212
00:11:41,320 --> 00:11:43,120
I won't be able to vent my hatred!

213
00:11:43,240 --> 00:11:45,140
Don't do that! Please reconsider, My Lord.

214
00:11:45,140 --> 00:11:47,540
It's impossible to kill Cheng Ruoning now.

215
00:11:48,380 --> 00:11:51,810
His Majesty has taken her
as his sworn sister.

216
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:53,500
What did you say?

217
00:11:54,480 --> 00:11:55,670
Here is the imperial decree.

218
00:11:55,670 --> 00:11:58,010
Cheng Ruoning,
the only daughter of the Cheng family,

219
00:11:58,010 --> 00:12:00,720
is intelligent, quick-witted,
virtuous and kind,

220
00:12:00,720 --> 00:12:03,710
having noble qualities
with a compassionate heart

221
00:12:03,740 --> 00:12:06,320
and showing concern for
the suffering of common people

222
00:12:06,320 --> 00:12:09,920
by donating her ancestral assets
to the imperial court generously,

223
00:12:09,180 --> 00:12:10,560
[Imperial Decree]

224
00:12:10,080 --> 00:12:11,980
which has greatly comforted my heart.

225
00:12:11,980 --> 00:12:14,240
I hereby take her
as my imperial sworn sister

226
00:12:14,240 --> 00:12:16,960
with the title of Princess Jiangning.

227
00:12:18,590 --> 00:12:20,840
Darn it! The money is gone,

228
00:12:21,020 --> 00:12:23,220
and that woman has even made a fool of me.

229
00:12:23,350 --> 00:12:25,800
Is everyone in the world against me?

230
00:12:26,100 --> 00:12:26,770
Fine.

231
00:12:27,630 --> 00:12:29,500
Since you all want to go against me,

232
00:12:29,500 --> 00:12:31,070
then I will show you

233
00:12:31,120 --> 00:12:33,170
who truly rules this country.

234
00:12:33,360 --> 00:12:34,430
Please calm down, My Lord.

235
00:12:34,430 --> 00:12:36,340
It's all because of Lu Chi and Shi Fa'ke.

236
00:12:36,340 --> 00:12:39,890
We should kill them as soon as possible.

237
00:12:39,910 --> 00:12:41,300
I have my own plans.

238
00:12:41,670 --> 00:12:44,780
Whether it's the Cheng family,
Lu Chi or Shi Fa'ke,

239
00:12:44,800 --> 00:12:46,510
no matter how much they struggle,

240
00:12:46,510 --> 00:12:48,270
they're just like mantises
trying to stop a chariot.

241
00:12:48,270 --> 00:12:49,910
Once I achieve my grand ambition,

242
00:12:49,910 --> 00:12:51,940
they will naturally bow to my power.

243
00:12:52,100 --> 00:12:53,500
How wise you are, My Lord!

244
00:12:53,610 --> 00:12:56,150
Since these people have failed to
recognize my favor,

245
00:12:56,150 --> 00:12:58,220
I will surely find the ones
who have discerning eyes

246
00:12:58,220 --> 00:13:00,200
to accomplish great things with me.

247
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:02,140
Only those who can laugh last

248
00:13:03,460 --> 00:13:04,860
will be the true winners.

249
00:13:05,960 --> 00:13:06,560
By the way,

250
00:13:07,760 --> 00:13:09,300
the King of Gaoyou State

251
00:13:09,350 --> 00:13:12,010
wants to let his dear daughter
marry that man.

252
