Unfortunately, the Princess of Gaoyou
escaped to the capital.

253
00:13:15,210 --> 00:13:17,340
Her whereabouts are currently unknown.

254
00:13:17,340 --> 00:13:21,250
We need to find the Princess of Gaoyou
as soon as possible.

255
00:13:21,470 --> 00:13:22,170
Yes.

256
00:13:25,320 --> 00:13:27,740
When the Cheng family gave the property
to the imperial court,

257
00:13:27,740 --> 00:13:29,870
I helped you two keep the Flower House.

258
00:13:30,020 --> 00:13:32,290
You can convert the Flower House
into a theater from now on.

259
00:13:32,290 --> 00:13:34,660
And Miss Cheng will continue
to manage the business.

260
00:13:34,660 --> 00:13:35,740
Then Young Master Qiujiang

261
00:13:35,740 --> 00:13:37,640
will no longer need to look elsewhere
to perform on stage.

262
00:13:37,640 --> 00:13:38,220
What do you think?

263
00:13:38,220 --> 00:13:40,110
That would be wonderful.

264
00:13:40,130 --> 00:13:42,510
Mr. Lu,
thank you for being so thoughtful.

265
00:13:42,740 --> 00:13:43,860
By the time
of the theater's opening ceremony,

266
00:13:43,860 --> 00:13:45,170
